name: The Unstable Cone: Vanilla
description: My first original ice cream cone, one of many to come. The Unstable Cone Series is more than a NFT, but a message for mental health. For me personally, I create these cones during a time of severely low mental health. These cones help me heal. My hope is that they provide a level of relatability and reassurance to you too. These cones are a reminder to reach out when you are suffering. You are not alone. There is light at the end of the tunnel.
